ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent excision of the uterine horn procedures performed.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Procedure. The intent of this value set is to identify patients who have had an excision of the uterine horn procedure.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with SNOMED CT codes identifying the excision of the uterine horn procedures by any approach.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
